<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to T2G!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .container {
      min-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .col-md-6 {
      width: 70%;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card welcome-card" style="background-color: #f5f5f5; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h1>Welcome to Sam' Tours</h1>
            <h3 class="card-title" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 10px;">Welcome aboard, <%=name%>!</h3>
            <p class="card-text" style="color: #333; line-height: 1.5;">We're thrilled to have you join our community at Sam's tours. We're confident you'll find value in every tour we have to offer.</p>
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
              <li class="list-group-item" style="border-color: transparent;">
                Explore our platform and discover the amazing features available to you.
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item" style="border-color: transparent;">
                <a href="#" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;">Get started guide</a> will help you navigate the basics.
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item" style="border-color: transparent;">
                Have questions or need help? Don't hesitate to reach out to our friendly <a href="#" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;">support team</a>.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
